z\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Hendrik Lorentz\">Hendrik Lorentz</a>, \n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Albert_Einstein\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Albert Einstein\">Albert Einstein</a>, \n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Langevin\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Paul Langevin\">Paul Langevin</a>,\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles-Eug%C3%A8ne_Guye\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Charles-Eugène Guye\">Charles-Eugène Guye</a>, \n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Thomson_Rees_Wilson\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Charles Thomson Rees Wilson\">Charles Thomson Rees Wilson</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Owen_Willans_Richardson\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Owen Willans Richardson\">Owen Willans Richardson</a>\n</p>\nThis picture is also available <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://w3.pppl.gov/~hammett/courses/gpp1/intro/solvay1927.html\">with names at the bottom</a>.", "source": "commons-desc-page"}, "DateTimeOriginal": {"value": "1927", "source": "commons-desc-page"}, "Credit": {"value": "<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://w3.pppl.gov/\">http://w3.pppl.gov/</a>\n</p>\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" data-mw-original-href=\"http://doi.org/10.3932/ethz-a-000046848\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.3932/ethz-a-000046848\">http://doi.org/10.3932/ethz-a-000046848</a>", "source": "commons-desc-page"}, "Artist": {"value": "<bdi><a href=\"https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q33206336\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"d:Q33206336\"><span title=\"French photographer\">Benjamin Couprie</span></a></bdi>", "source": "commons-desc-page"}, "LicenseShortName": {"value": "Public domain", "source": "commons-desc-page", "hidden": ""}, "UsageTerms": {"value": "Public domain", "source": "commons-desc-page"}, "AttributionRequired": {"value": "false", "source": "commons-desc-page", "hidden": ""}, "Copyrighted": {"value": "False", "source": "commons-desc-page", "hidden": ""}, "Restrictions": {"value": "", "